phphard is a PHP source code static analyzer. Its aim is to strong type PHP
programs and detect bugs at compile time.

Pretty printing of PHP programs is also supported.

This is a work in progress and currently (2013-10-16) only a small subset
of PHP is supported.

How to build
============

ocamlbuild -I src phphard.native

How to run
==========

cat ./test/test3.php | ./phphard.native

How to clean
============

ocamlbuild -clean
